{"tid":2296561,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【10大藍籌】嘉湖山坑劈穿480萬 今期最低價","createTime":"2020-11-22T14:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T02:36:54.000Z","uid":73269,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10b3773ceb1da475389623b31de2dca9601df6e6","tid":2296561,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"嘉湖山莊11月暫22宗成交 2房跌穿500萬 今期最低價<br />\n<br />\n買家為外區投資客，入市預算約500萬元，兩個月前已在市區睇樓，但可選擇的單位不多，遂轉移目標，認為嘉湖山莊為10大藍籌屋苑之首，買賣及租務市場相對穩定，參觀上址後感合適，即場還價洽購，見業主肯由502萬減至<span class=\"red\">480</span>萬，故即時決定入市。"},{"pid":"386fb3f135e187dab0edbed6a0356eed35ebb2df","tid":2296561,"uid":326526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T15:49:44.000Z","msg":"低層無景又向西北嘅𠴱啲咪講啦<br />\n<br />\n都話唔計囉"},{"pid":"45b107259694c608e08b27b5afa0a78d34858280","tid":2296561,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"向西北食正西北風梗係平啲㗎喎"},{"pid":"7ac02aaa8fd9dce178ae805a5b27809c94dbf527","tid":2296561,"uid":73269,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"45b107259694c608e08b27b5afa0a78d34858280","tid":2296561,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"向西北食正西北風梗係平啲㗎喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"唔計，ok?"},{"pid":"4234b45f5623047231edf787d17cd4a7725e8eed","tid":2296561,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T23:58:00.000Z","msg":"呎價呢？"},{"pid":"72d4c973e3adc00dba6c4e4faf61195824083ebc","tid":2296561,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:01:35.000Z","msg":"其實減得少"},{"pid":"0ebf8c49871b7f5e88c3b78017c034554bf5b4ea","tid":2296561,"uid":92125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:02:45.000Z","msg":"嘉湖唔計"},{"pid":"e214dd9a5b2b875ae4dc585c0aaff12c0c34c0dd","tid":2296561,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:06:44.000Z","msg":"嘉